name: #6 MALICE
description: Once a Hunter with many victories to share, now a rogue hunted by his own. A rebel in nature Malice never waits for him to be found, he searches the Etheral plains to find the Hunters, vowed to punish the ones who dare to go against him. Dictator of the Dungeons of Death he tortured Hunters for centuries taking pleasure with every scream. Blood is Marked on the walls to warn those who dared to enter, to turn back if they cherish the life they live.
